[1.035, "o", "\u001b[90m│\u001b[39m\r\r\n\u001b[90m└\u001b[39m  Installed 56 commands to /Users/willi/.agent-instructions-demo-workspace/my-project/.opencode/commands\r\r\nInstalled 2 skills to /Users/willi/.agent-instructions-demo-workspace/my-project/.opencode/skills\r\r\n\r\r\nRestart your agent (OpenCode or Claude Code) to pick up the new commands.\r\r\n\r\r\nTry it out:\r\r\n\r\r\n  /kata                  → Pick a practice challenge\r\r\n  /red 1 returns \"1\"     → Write first failing test for your kata\r\r\n  /green                 → Make it pass\r\r\n\r\r\nSee a full example: https://github.com/wbern/agent-instructions#example-conversations\r\r\n\r\r\nTo automate this setup:\r\r\n  agent-instructions --scope=project --agent=both --commands=spike.md,tdd.md,red.md,green.md,refactor.md,cycle.md,simplify.md,tdd-review.md,issue.md,create-issues.md,commit.md,busycommit.md,pr.md,summarize.md,gap.md,code-review.md,polish.md,worktree-setup.md,worktree-add.md,worktree-cleanup.md,beepboop.md,add-command.md,kata.md,create-adr.md,research.md,commit-hook-checklist.md,upgrade-deps.md,g"]
